LDA will collaborate with WGU’s Program Experience Futures Team to explore and refine
innovative methodologies for competency-based education. The primary focus is the
development and testing of insights around the LDA Cognitive Task Analysis (CTA) Tool,
integrating learner context refinement, synthetic testing, tool prototyping and other research
and analysis as described in this SOW (the, “Project”). CTA tool is the focus of this project’s
exploration which can be used as future foundational guidance to support future
implementations. The goal is to generate horizon-focused insights that will inform WGU’s
decision-making regarding tool adoption and strategic innovation, rather than delivering an
out-of-the-box tool.
Insights and recommendations provided from this project will inform WGU’s strategic decisionmaking
about tool adoption, integration strategies, and long-term innovations
